'''Aurek-Bacta''' was the designation of a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] rally point in [[Murkhana City/Legends|Murkhana City]] during the [[Battle of Murkhana (Clone Wars)|Battle]] of [[Murkhana/Legends|Murkhana]]. At this point, [[Clone Commander/Legends|Clone Commander]] [[Salvo (clone trooper)|Salvo]] ordered [[Climber (clone)|Climber]] and [[Ion Team]] to set an ambush for [[Roan Shryne]] at the rally point. Climber, disbelieving [[Order 66/Legends|Order 66]], instead ambushed Salvo and incapacitated him while Shryne escaped.<ref name="Rise of Darth Vader">''[[Dark Lord: The Rise of Darth Vader]]''</ref>

